# 🔐 Smart Door Lock System

An IoT-enabled smart lock that allows remote control via a mobile app, enhancing home security using ESP32 and a solenoid lock.

## ⚙️ Technologies Used
- ESP32 microcontroller
- Blynk mobile app
- Arduino IDE
- Relay Module
- Solenoid Lock

## 🔑 Features
- Remote lock/unlock control from smartphone
- Real-time status monitoring
- Secure hardware integration
- WiFi-enabled connectivity

## 🛠️ Setup Instructions
1. Connect ESP32 with Relay + Solenoid Lock.
2. Upload Arduino sketch using Arduino IDE.
3. Configure Blynk app with authentication token.
4. Connect ESP32 to WiFi and control the lock via Blynk.

